msgid ""
"The base data model every Bades.id workspace runs on.\n"
"\n"
"#### What \"foundation\" means\n"
"\n"
"Every Bades.id workspace starts with this set of objects. They define the shape of your CRM, including relationships, activity, and reporting. Everything else, including marketplace apps, AI agents, and custom objects, plugs into them.\n"
"\n"
"#### Included objects\n"
"- **Residents & Households**: contact and account records\n"
"- **Services: village service requests\n"
"- **Notes & Tasks**: activity and follow-ups\n"
"- **Workflows & Dashboards**: automation and reporting\n"
"\n"
"Remove this app and the rest of Bades.id has nothing to hang off.\n"
"\n"
"#### Build your own app\n"
"\n"
"Extend Bades.id with your own objects, fields, logic functions, or AI skills. Scaffold a new app in one command:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"npx create-bades-app@latest my-bades-app\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Then inside the folder:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"cd my-bades-app\n"
"yarn twenty dev\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"See the [Getting Started guide](https://bades.id/developers/extend/apps/getting-started) for the full walkthrough, and [Building Apps](https://bades.id/developers/extend/apps/building) for the `defineApplication` / `defineEntity` APIs."
msgstr ""
"The base data model every Bades.id workspace runs on.\n"
"\n"
